title: Light Filled unit in the heart of Inner Sunset
posting_body: ['DESCRIPTION', 'This is a new 3BR, 1BA apartment in a newly constructed building.', 'The apartment contains many upgrades such as large bedrooms, modern bathrooms, elegant light fixtures, an in-unit washer/dryers, and a large kitchen stocked with stainless steel appliances.', 'Located near all the neighborhood amenities, public library, public transportation, and corporate shuttle buses.', 'AT-A-GLANCE', 'Bedrooms: 3BR Bathrooms: 1BA', 'Parking: Street', 'Lease Duration: 1 Year', 'Pet Policy: Dogs and Cats Under 40 Lbs.', '- Non-Aggressive Breeds OK', 'Laundry:', 'In-Unit', 'Storage: bonus storage area in the basement', 'VIDEO TOUR', '<URL>', 'APARTMENT AMENITIES', 'Newly Remodeled Modern floors Large Bedrooms', 'One large detached bathroom Stainless Steel Appliances - Range/Oven, Refrigerator, Dishwasher Large Closets Washer/Dryer in unit LED Recessed Lighting', 'Throughout', 'LOCATION', "Short walking distance to restaurants and stores on Irving Street, Andronico's (Safeway) Community Markets, Sunset Branch Public Library and Golden Gate Park - Mother's", 'Meadow Playground -Public', 'Transportation: 2 blocks from N-Judah streetcar, steps away from bus routes 7 Haight/Noreiga, 28 19th Avenue, and 29 Sunset.', '-Easy access to corporate shuttle buses on 19th Avenue -Close to UCSF, SF State University, and Stonetown Galleria (shopping mall) -Easy access to 280 S.', 'LEASE TERMS', '12-Month Lease Terms Shorter Term Leases Available Upon Request Utilities paid by tenants Non-smoking Available now Showings by Appointment Only']
